Question",name:"How does Mastodon scheduling work?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:'\n          <p>With Buffer’s Mastodon scheduler, you can plan, collaborate, schedule, and publish content that drives meaningful engagement and growth for your brand. Some of our favorite features include:</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>Customizable <a href="https://support.buffer.com/hc/en-us/articles/360036232053-Setting-up-your-Posting-Schedule?utm_source=marketing-site&utm_medium=help-center&utm_campaign=help-center">posting schedules</a></li>\n            <li>Publishing capabilities for all sorts of media, including videos, images, and more</li>\n            <li>A composer that allows you to craft a different message for each social network</li>\n            <li>Crossposting capabilities, which allow you to easily share posts to <a href="/facebook">Facebook</a>, <a href="/x">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href="/threads">Threads</a>, <a href="/linkedin">LinkedIn</a>, and more</li>\n            <li>A <a href="/create">Create Space</a> that allows you to save your post ideas and come back to them later</li>\n            <li><a href="https://support.buffer.com/article/585-creating-and-managing-campaigns?utm_source=marketing-site&utm_medium=help-center&utm_campaign=help-center">Tags</a> to help you sort and organize your content by theme or category</li>\n            <li>A <a href="https://support.buffer.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039028273-Installing-and-using-the-Buffer-Browser-Extension?utm_source=marketing-site&utm_medium=help-center&utm_campaign=help-center">browser extension</a> to quickly share content from anywhere on the web</li>\n            <li>A <a href="https://support.buffer.com/hc/en-us/articles/360038640494-Creating-managing-and-approving-draft-posts?utm_source=marketing-site&utm_medium=help-center&utm_campaign=help-center">drafts and approval process</a> to easily collaborate with your team</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p>Just to name a few!</p>\n        '}},{"@type":"Question",name:"What types of Mastodon posts can I schedule with Buffer?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:"\n          <p>We currently support text (up to 500 characters), link preview, image, GIF, and video posts. You can spruce up your posts with links, hashtags, and mentions, too.</p>\n        "}},{"@type":"Question",name:"Can I schedule Mastodon posts to publish automatically?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:"\n          <p>Yes, Buffer automatically publishes your Mastodon posts for the scheduled time you set.</p>\n        "}},{"@type":"Question",name:"How many posts can I schedule to Mastodon?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:"\n          <p>With our free plan, you can schedule up to 10 posts at a time. Need more? All our paid plans let you schedule up to 2,000 posts, starting at $5 per month. There is no monthly, or yearly limit.</p>\n        "}},{"@type":"Question",name:"How do I start scheduling my Mastodon posts?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:'\n          <p>You can start scheduling your Mastodon posts by signing up to our free plan or <a href="https://login.buffer.com/signup?product=buffer&plan=team&cycle=year">trial our premium features free for 14 days</a>. Once you’ve signed up, connect your Mastodon server, log into your Mastodon account, and then start scheduling to your profile immediately.</p>\n        '}},{"@type":"Question",name:"Is Buffer an AI tool?",acceptedAnswer:{"@type":"Answer",text:'\n          <p>No. Like our other channels, Buffer’s AI assistant can be used to help suggest new ideas or your refine your posts. But it’s entirely optional. Your posts are not automatically generated, changed, or tweaked by the AI. The AI Assistant is a standalone feature — Buffer is not an AI tool, and all our core features (posting, scheduling, planning, and more) aren’t AI-powered. You can <a href="/ai-assistant">learn more about how AI Assistant works</a>.</p>\n        '}}]},w=a(10400),b=a(87445),x=a.n(b),_=a(42654);let 